Name: Escape the Room
Description: Do you have enough wits to escape the room? If yes then this is the best challenge for you. Filled with mind boggling games and puzzles, this experience will give you enough knots in your mind and is sure to leave you and your friends with a puzzling memory. Come on everybody and join us at Himalaya on the 7th of February to leave your minds in a twist.

Name: Treasure Hunt
Description: Embark on an enthralling hunt which will test your wits with mind-boggling clues. Compete against various teams and be the first ones to get your hands on the treasure. Be a part of the most exhilarating treasure hunt of the year and get a chance to prove your mettle and take home some sweet loot. Sign up here : https://tinyurl.com/Trailofblood

Name: Bike Stunts Show
Description: Does Road Rash bring back old memories? Ever wanted to do bike stunts like that in real life? Come on then and join us at the NBH road at 2:30pm and witness spectacular performances by our skilled stuntmen. We are sure you shall relish the antics displayed by these daredevils!! Also, do NOT try these at home ;)

Name: Stargazing
Description: We all know how hectic each day is in the life of an engineering student can be... But have you ever wanted to simply lie down in the grass and peacefully just watch the stars above on a clear night...If so, then this is just the event for you. Do come, because we will make sure that this one of the events that you shall take back with you for another 4 years and perhaps your life!!

Name: Roadblock
Description: Science and music have a reputation for going hand in hand. If you are one of those 20th century kids who is simply in love with music, then this event by Felicity is for you. Road-Rash is the street performance which will leave you dazzled and you would want it to never end.....Join us at at 3pm on NBH road and witness the melodious music brought to you by the students of IIIT.

Name: Battle of Brains: Subtle Curry Quiz
Description: So you call yourself a nerd? Do your friends call you a geek? But do you have it in you to compete in one of the biggest quizzes ever? Welcome to the Quiz Club, where we promise to put to test all that knowledge youâve acquired over the years . At every question, connect and pounce. May the best nerd win!

Name: Lit Charades
Description: Did you like to play charades with your friends in school? Do you have more fandom merch than normal apparel? Do you have a million theme songs stuck in your head? Do you relate more to sonnets than you ever did to rap songs or upbeat music? If yes, then the Lit Club presents to you the Lit Charades - a mixture of the old friendly game and literary knowledge to give you the most fun that you will ever have. May the best biblophile win!!

Name: Robo Race
Description: Interested in building and designing robots? Does the show battle bots bring back old memories? If yes then this is the event for you as here you to get to test the efficiency and power, skills of your droid/robot. Test your and your bots mettle on the race track by reaching the finish line on your own(or you can knock out the others) and earn exciting prizes and also pave your way to becoming the greatest robotics engineer on the planet!

Name: Break-in-CTF
Description: Ever wanted to hack Google? Showoff your skills by deciphering some of the hardest encrypted messages and in return master the art of decoding and move forward on your path of becoming one of the best hackers/decoders in the world.

Name: Codecraft
Description: Does coding enthrall you? Are you one of those rare people who is overjoyed by the mention of OJ? This event of felicity is one that is much more fun than just boring math questions... Code-craft brings to you a simple yet elegant competitive programming challenge with basic logic embedded in spicy story lines... Come along with a open mind and bring your friends too to compete with!!

Name: Singularity
Description: Ever thought that your knowledge of computer science and food could get you to the top? If not then, then you are in for a surprise as IIIT hosts Singularity- a machine learning challenge where you have use your skills in machine learning to correctly identify what food is present in a photo but just don't start drooling as their is more. Participate now so that you can earn a chance to win upto Rs 40K cash prize.

Name: FAIL! Talks
Description: Failure isn't fun , but is an opportunity to learn, reflect and regroup. Started at the Massachusetts Institute of Technology with professors from MIT and the Ivy League colleges as past speakers, FAIL! has now reached Asia at IIIT Hyderabad. Fail! is a platform to face the moments of failure head on,sharing them and most importantly improving by them . It's a celebration of moments we don't generally talk about. Come join us on the journey of ups and downs, listening to person's failures , thinking of ways to get out of them , learning new ways of life and most importantly to have fun!

Name: Parliamentary debate (Day 3)
Description: Have you ever felt oppressed by some policy , felt any injustice or wanted change any policy ? Are you a kind of person who loves to make voice against something troubling you, pointing out the mistake of persons ? If you feel any of these traits inside you , Parliamentary debate is the event for you . Come join us to discuss,mock different policies and (hopefully!) reach to a conclusion ! Debating is the way to clear out thoughts, gather self contentment if something is troubling you form within.

Name: Footbids
Description: Always wondered what high stakes auctions are like? Well now is the chance to channel your inner football team owner! E-Cell IIITH proudly presents FOOTBIDS, a full-blown football auction! You'll be given a budget; utilize your resources to buy the best players you can and maximize your chances of winning. Everybody will make a team of 11 players, which will then fight in a stimulated elimination style tournament. Remember prizes worth 3K are on stake.

Name: DigiHunt: Bang Head Here
Description: Want to challenge your thinking capacity and concepts, have fun and win some exciting prizes? Well now is the time ! Come to the DigiHunt where the winner takes it all. Challenge yourself to the extreme and make the use of time to win! Because the clock is always ringing!

Proudly present your best snaps and get a chance to take home the title of Best Photographer home.

Name: PUBG competition
Description: Chicken Dinner!! These two words are known by every child of this century. Think that you are good t the video game? Well come on and find out as you go up against some of the most skillful and gruesome players that ever walked(or drove) the Lands of PUBG. Be the last man standing and be declared as the King of the Battlegrounds or you can also eat some lovely chicken dinner.

Name: Data Science Workshop
Description: Ask a dozen people what âdata scienceâ means, and you get back thirteen different answers. This vagueness is unfortunately accompanied with a lot of hype and misaligned expectations. In this workshop, we aim to mitigate this by taking a good look under the hood of data science. This is meant for everybody who wants to know what data science is (and isnât) about. Even when youâll never intend to work with data yourself, it can be eye-opening to have experienced it. Caution: thereâs a chance youâll want to learn more afterwards!
